      "chinese": "對族人而言，族名是祖先的遺產，代表個人身分、地位、社會階級；漢名亦如是，是父母對我們的期望與祝福。每個小孩出生，父母會邀集雙方家屬及部落相關人士，與大家分享家中添子的喜悅，為孩子命名，只要大家形成共識，即可公開受理稱呼。",
      "ab": "kai nagane ki Ngudradrekai, baai pasuhu ki cucungulaneta, sapatuthingala ku takaumawmasa si tatakaenena, kai ciniyukukana ka nagane miyalri ka sasyadradrama sasubulrubulruwa ki mahudrawdrange. lu kitulalake ku lrulai, aitaha sunagane, ku pimahudrawdranga si mahudrawdrange ki tamudaananemadu si nipasusuwa ki cekele, madawdaulu si ikai ki sakiahagailini sunagane, sana kahathudu pwataluvaivai suanagane.",
